Cascading stylesheets is used for website layout
inline CSS : style page directly in the html element inside the head tag
internal CSS:we style the page using  <style> tag within a single document.

External CSS: style the page using external CSS fill example.css file

css format

selector    property            value
   a     {  background-color:  yellow;   }

 web safe fonts are fonts that we do not need to import from website
 we simply can apply to our text.

 we can set margin use three ways

 A.     { margin-top:5px ;     B  { margin:5px(top) 10px(right) 5px(bottom) 10px(left)
         margin-bottom: 5px;   /method C is used if the opposite side have the same margin
        margin-right: 10px;     C {margin: 5px(top and bottom) 10px(right and left)}
        margin-left: 10px; }

positioning

static is the default  positioning
Relative is the position relative to the default position
fixed is a position which can not bi hidden when we scroll the web.
initial return to original position
Inherit this inherits the position of the parent tag.
